
run index.html file directly using live server make sure internet is connected and stable...

Spinovix App/
├── index.html             # entry point ( home page code) main file of website
|
├── assets/                # Folder for storing all images , videos , gif directly in this folder
│
├── css/                   # Folder for all CSS files
│   └── styles.css         # global styles common
│   └── contact.css
│   └── home.css
│   └── solution.css
│
├── js/                    # Folder for all JavaScript files
│   └── header.js
│   └── footer.js
│   └── form.js            # contact form functions
│   └── Marquee.js         # Marquee effect of home page solutions section
│   └── testimonal.js
│   └── tailwind.config.js  # tailwind configuration file
│
├── components/            # Folder for main pages
│  └ Solution/              # Folder for Solution page
│    └── solution.html
|
│  └ Contact/              # Folder for Contact page
│    └── contact.html
